Changes with plumbca 0.4

  - Change: optimize the fetch method of Collection class in collection module that extract the metadata query operation from _fetch_expired method to the fetch method, so that decrease the calls of the metadata query.
  - Change: adding parameters option to the return for the query and fetch method of Collection class in collection module.


(11 Oct 2015) Changes with plumbca 0.3

  - Feature: refactor the datastruct of metadata and the relative handling logic.
  - Feature: adding new SortedCountCollection and UniqueCountCollection class.
